# List of words to mimic the hissing phonics of Parseltongue (snake language):


'Greetings & Basics'
"Sss" - Hello
"Hiss" - Yes
"Sssss" - No
"Ssssst" - Thank you
"Sssssss" - Goodbye
"Sssssssst" - Please
"Hissss" - I am sorry
"Ssssssssss" - I do not understand
"Ssssssssttt" - Excuse me
"Hisssss" - I love you
"Sah" - My name is
"Seh" - How are you?
"Sil" - I am fine, thank you.
"Sssah" - Friend


